You can simply ask Alexa to control your Della+ products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Della+” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “Della+” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Della+” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Della+” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Della+” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the bedroom air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off the bedroom air conditioner.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, set bedroom light to green.
